{"tid":1781481,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"而家唔係分化嘅時候","createTime":"2019-12-13T07:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T12:20:20.000Z","uid":239942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b8ceba23ae3b065671c033aed2fc5d02f2ce01e2","tid":1781481,"uid":239942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:39:52.000Z","msg":"想同大家講聲對唔住<br />\n之前開左個post比大家以為我想分化<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港人當中都有唔同派系<br />\n泛黄光譜都有民主獨立之分<br />\n但面對中共港共嘅共同壓逼<br />\n<br />\n我地冇分化嘅理由<br />\n民主派支持者希望你地將來可以唔好調轉槍頭打壓港獨<br />\n獨立派希望你地可以忍一忍，集中五大訴求先<br />\n贏左呢仗再打獨立戰<br />\n<br />\n香港人團結 香港人assemble<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cc82f6eea7b7a43310a8dafc1448229ee01ea3","tid":1781481,"uid":239942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:40:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25d99a26a11d225e8a2cade9e12955bec5229f13","tid":1781481,"uid":239942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5cc82f6eea7b7a43310a8dafc1448229ee01ea3","tid":1781481,"uid":239942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:40:28.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:40:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c600ffa5325d60d29f5b770421fa13d07221e63e","tid":1781481,"uid":239942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:41:07.000Z","msg":"同各位手足道歉"},{"pid":"8305f18392ed4022eadd9dfef57dc5d3d3f3cfb5","tid":1781481,"uid":239942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:43:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9dd229c29daee07f1224ab45ea58e1ff4d593d1a","tid":1781481,"uid":239942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:45:54.000Z","msg":"正能量post"},{"pid":"56653e16ac3abe9ea91caf5fbe2596abb10256aa","tid":1781481,"uid":239942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:50:48.000Z","msg":"推啊屌 正經post冇人理"},{"pid":"eea98a736bb89ad832ed8a4cd2331613cd80ac